---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
import BackgroundCanvas from '../components/BackgroundCanvas';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact - Smooth Plugins">
    <BackgroundCanvas client:only="react" />
    <div class="layout-container">
        <Navigation active="Contact" />

        <Card
            title="Get in Touch"
            kicker="Contact Me"
            variant="blue"
            span={12}
        >
            <p class="card-desc">Have questions about Smooth Plugins? Need help with integration? Want to collaborate? Or just want to chat about why JavaScript is both beautiful and terrifying? I'd love to hear from you!</p>
        </Card>

        <Card title="The Contact Form Saga" kicker="Plot Twist" variant="white" span={8}>
            <div class="coming-soon-message">
                <div class="emoji-hero">üöß ‚òï üíª</div>
                <h3>One Person, Infinite To-Do List</h3>
                <p>Turns out when you're a one-person company, building a contact form ranks just below "optimize that thing that's already fast" and "refactor code that already works perfectly."</p>
                <p>But hey, I'm a software artisan! I appreciate the beauty of a well-crafted email or a thoughtful LinkedIn message. In fact, I prefer it‚Äîno form validation errors, no CAPTCHAs asking if a stop sign is actually a stop sign.</p>
                <div class="fun-fact">
                    <strong>Real Talk:</strong> I actually respond to emails. Like, personally. No chatbots, no automated responses. Just me, caffeine, and an inbox that I check way too often.
                </div>
                <p class="coming-soon-note">So go ahead‚Äîdrop me a line! I promise I don't bite (unless you're a memory leak).</p>
            </div>
        </Card>

        <Card title="Let's Connect!" kicker="Reach Out" variant="lavender" span={4}>
            <div class="contact-methods">
                <div class="contact-method">
                    <span class="method-icon">üìß</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Email</strong>
                        <a href="mailto:sakib3201@gmail.com">sakib3201@gmail.com</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="contact-method">
                    <span class="method-icon">üíº</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>LinkedIn</strong>
                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sakib-shahon/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Drop a message</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="contact-method">
                    <span class="method-icon">üêô</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>GitHub</strong>
                        <a href="https://github.com/sakib3201/smoothplugins" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View repository</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="contact-method">
                    <span class="method-icon">üí°</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Ideas?</strong>
                        <a href="https://github.com/sakib3201/smoothplugins/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Share on GitHub</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Card>

        <Card title="Response Time" kicker="Realistic Expectations" variant="peach" span={6}>
            <div class="hours-info">
                <p>I'm just one person juggling code, coffee, and the occasional existential crisis about semicolons. But I do my best to respond quickly!</p>
                <div class="hours-list">
                    <div class="hours-item">
                        <strong>Usually Within</strong>
                        <span>24-48 hours (sometimes faster if I'm already glued to my screen)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hours-item">
                        <strong>Working Hours</strong>
                        <span>Flexible (perks of being your own boss!)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hours-item">
                        <strong>Weekend Emails</strong>
                        <span>Sent? Yes. Regretted? Also yes.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Card>

        <Card title="Found a Security Issue?" kicker="Responsible Disclosure" variant="black" span={6}>
            <div class="security-info">
                <p>If you've discovered a security vulnerability, please report it privately to:</p>
                <a href="mailto:sakib3201@gmail.com" class="security-email">sakib3201@gmail.com</a>
                <p class="security-note">Subject line: "Security Issue - [Brief Description]". I take security seriously and will respond ASAP. Please don't disclose issues publicly until I've had a chance to fix them. Thanks for keeping things secure!</p>
            </div>
        </Card>

        <Footer />
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .coming-soon-message {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
    }

    .emoji-hero {
        font-size: 48px;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .coming-soon-message h3 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--c-text-primary);
        margin: 0;
    }

    .coming-soon-message p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--c-text-secondary);
        margin: 0;
    }

    .fun-fact {
        padding: 20px;
        background: var(--c-bg);
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 2px dashed var(--c-border);
        margin: 8px 0;
    }

    .fun-fact strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--c-text-primary);
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .coming-soon-note {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--c-text-secondary);
        padding-top: 12px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    }

    .contact-methods {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 24px;
    }

    .contact-method {
        display: flex;
        gap: 16px;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .method-icon {
        font-size: 28px;
    }

    .contact-method strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .contact-method a {
        color: var(--c-text-secondary);
        font-size: 14px;
        text-decoration: underline;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .contact-method a:hover {
        color: var(--c-text-primary);
    }

    .hours-info {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
    }

    .hours-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
    }

    .hours-item {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 4px;
        padding: 16px;
        background: var(--c-bg);
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    }

    .hours-item strong {
        font-size: 15px;
    }

    .hours-item span {
        color: var(--c-text-secondary);
        font-size: 14px;
    }

    .hours-item a {
        color: var(--c-text-primary);
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .security-info {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
    }

    .security-email {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background: var(--c-white);
        color: var(--c-black);
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
        text-align: center;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .security-email:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    }

    .security-note {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .coming-soon-message h3 {
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .emoji-hero {
            font-size: 36px;
        }
    }
</style>
